title: Available Commands
body: OPS Team 53.  Sorry to pull you away from home during the Holidays.  We have a burned out building in Bearclaw with a 10 foot skeleton. It is the ONLY building in Bearclaw.  Your Mission is to Investigate the Scene, Obfuscate any Evidence, and End anything Unnatural.  Good Luck.    Please enter command - malcomestates.exe
